 not follow instructions.<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE FONT START--><span style="color:yellow;"><!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>Upon zone in run immedietly West (left) to the wall.  Do not wait or hesitate</em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END-->.</span><!--EZCODE FONT END--><br>
<br>
The first major wipe we had was due to people waiting at the top of the port in hill, and /or running the wrong way then back to the safespot thinkign they had no agro.<br>
<br>
Problem was they DID have agro.  Mobs have insanly large agro radiuses in Fear and some are line of sight agro especially for those under level 60.  Therefore you can have agro from a mob you don't even see.  Also the port in hill is an instant agro increaser as well.<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE FONT START--><span style="color:yellow;"><!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>If you are randomly teleported, lay down and die.  Do not train the SS</em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END-->.</span><!--EZCODE FONT END--><br>
<br>
The second major wipe we have had was due specifically to people training the safe spot.  This was observed by me and a few others.  Specifically 3 people in particualr were responsible for the wipe, one person having trained the SS a total of 3 times that I saw.<br>
<br>
Some mobs randomly teleport you to random spots in the zone.  The higher your level, the shorter the distance.  See statement above about agro.  People were running back to the SS WITH FULL TRAINS BEHIND THEM.  SO hence the new policy:<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em><!--EZCODE FONT START--><span style="color:yellow;">If you find you run the wrong way OR are randomly teleported to a spot in the zone, you will stand and cout to five.  If you are not attacked, you may make your way back to the SS, checking all the time to see if you have agro.  If you are attacked at any time, you WILL Lay down and die, getting a loc of your corpse for retrieval.  <br>
<br>
If you are caught training the safe spot, you will be TLed out of the raid immedietly.  You will then be put on a probationary period of 3 months during which time you will not be eleigle for epic drops and can not attend any raid which has a safe spot</span><!--EZCODE FONT END--></em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> <p><!--EZCODE BR START--><br /><!--EZCODE BR END--><br>
